{
  "stem": "17426.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 180.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A wonderful play.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I can't remember the name of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I can really remember the whole dialogue yet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I attended the Dobra Public School.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I attended the Jewish gymnasium in Kalisz and a dental Institute in Kalisz beyond this for one year.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, my favorite Jewish holiday was Tisha B'Av.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because on Tisha B'Av, we could throw these little things, these little things that grow on bushes that stick to the clothes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what they're called in English.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had some [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What is it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Thorns, that's right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was a child's game.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We could throw them, and we could not be regarded as someone unruly doing this, because this was the sort of thing that we did.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course I liked very much after [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Passover, where we had nuts in temple, where we throw nuts over the Torahs, and everyone got [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was something very special for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Our holidays were very, very well-observed, that is totally observed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father would take us by our hands, lead us to the temple.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We'd sit around him, and he would have time for us at that point.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he would put his hand on our heads and put his-- do his blessings and sort of show his real love, which he did not have much time to show during other times.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so did my mother when we came home from shul.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She would ask how shul was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she would sit separately from my father, upstairs, she could not sit with my father.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was not allowed in those days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so these were the precious days that I remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a smaller bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
